Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <gilardh> @MorganJekyll Regarding HUSH messaging app, we have put a few bricks on SilenceDragonAndroid (SDA) and SilentDragonLite (SDL). We are working hard to strengthen network security and eradicate metadata leaks. A secure and private base is important for building private messaging applications, which is our goal.
